{"tid":1684213,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"仲有5日就到全民口罩日喇！！！！","createTime":"2019-10-31T03:38:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T07:58:09.000Z","uid":27026,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"de520547dfd534a51b205990fb0d67d1966f903f","tid":1684213,"uid":27026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:38:31.000Z","msg":"為咗宣傳11.5全民口罩日，我會每日都會開一個po倒數同提醒大家果日戴口罩，務求令到果日我要見到個個戴晒口罩返工返學放工放學！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n原本戴開嘅就繼續戴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家可以做嘅野就係手人置頂呢個po，打個「推」、push、貼文宣圖等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">11.5 全民口罩日！！！！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uvmPiAF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuvmPiAF.jpg&h=e4c989ff&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qjcnDAF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqjcnDAF.jpg&h=fa5622a1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oWT6kO0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoWT6kO0.jpg&h=a94d3e2e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sktBH2k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsktBH2k.jpg&h=83c94ef3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2iRon2m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2iRon2m.jpg&h=010b2be7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JguJn2m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJguJn2m.jpg&h=b9b99bc6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SHs3n2m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/